{{define "content"}}{{- /*gotype:github.com/mdhender/ottoweb/components/app/pages/reports.Content_t*/ -}}
<p class="mt-6 text-l leading-8">
    OttoWeb is a work in progress and the reports upload process is being improved.
    If you like things the way they were, you can still use the original upload page.
    If you like change and don't use drag and drop, please try the new plain text upload page.
</p>

<br>

<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pb-5">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">The Original</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        The original upload page supports both drag and drop and copy+paste for plain text files.
        It works but it is a bit clunky.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        Please click <a href="/reports/uploads" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">here</a> to use the original upload page.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pb-5">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">New Plain Text Upload (experimental)</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        The new plain text upload page features a text box for pasting your turn report and an "improved" workflow.
        You have the option to "scrub" the report to fix some common errors before uploading it.
        It does yet not support drag and drop.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        <strong>EXPERIMENTAL</strong>.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        Please click <a href="/reports/uploads/plain-text" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">here</a> to test the updated plain text report upload page.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pb-5">
    <h3 class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">Upload Word documents (experimental)</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        This page implements a drag and drop control for uploading Word documents.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        <strong>EXPERIMENTAL</strong>.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-sm text-gray-500">
        Please click <a href="/reports/dropbox/upload" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">here</a> to test the Word document drag and drop page.
    </p>
</div>
{{end}}

